==English==
===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[plumbum|plumb(um)]]'', lead + '''[[-ic]]'''

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-notcomp}}

#{{chemistry}} Of, pertaining to, resembling or containing [[lead]].
#{{chemistry}} Specifically, of [[compound]]s in which it has a higher [[valence]] as contrasted with [[plumbous]] compounds.

